ique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"map-loading-error"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"dataId"},{"type":"text","text":" parameter in the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"type":"text","text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"each batch will be included in the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"call, the data ID in the "},{"code":"source-data-loaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note","name":"Note"},{"name":"Throws","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError"},{"text":" if there is a problem updating features in the source.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"aside","style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/stylemanager\/updategeojsonsourcefeatures(forsourceid:features:dataid:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\